Package: PLFD
Type: Package
Title: A Portmanteau Local Feature Discrimination Approach to the High-Dimensional Matrix-Variate Data
Version: 0.9
Date: 2019-11-11
Author: Zengchao XU, Shan Luo, Zehua Chen
Maintainer: Zengchao XU <xuzengchao@sjtu.edu.cn>
Description: Identify the local features that are significant to classification and employ them
    to form sub-discriminant functions, then aggregate the subfunctions for classification.
